Renown female DJ Pierra Makena has cancelled her summer heat USA tour to take care of her ailing daughter Rica Pokot. The mother of one shared a video from her daughter's hospital bed asking her fans to pray for the child. She explained that her daughter has been unwell for some time but her condition had worsened. She went on to apologise to her fans in Minnesota and Dallas, and said that she would announce a later travel date. "My current situation. I was meant to be on a flight today to the US. But here I am. My baby has been unwell and just got worse," she wrote. "I ask for your understanding and prayers and all the other cities after this weekend kindly bare with me....but we shall do this gain." Pierraâ€™s fans have sent her well wishes and prayers for her daughter on the comment section.